    "  - All claims truthful and properly authorized\n\n",
    "❌ PROHIBITED:\n",
    "  - False references to King/Queen/heir/regent\n",
    "  - Claims of royal endorsement without authorization\n",
    "  - Unauthorized use of royal symbols/imagery\n\n",
    "Evaluate this claim: ", claimText, "\n\n",
    "Question: Does this claim FALSELY REFER to the monarchy without proper\n",
    "authorization, or inappropriately use royal references in advertising?\n\n",
    "Answer with:\n",
    "- YES (violates monarchy rules - prohibited) or NO (acceptable)\n",
    "- Confidence: [0-100]%\n",
    "- Reasoning: [1-2 sentences explaining your judgment]"

// PROMPT 16: Giveaway/Contest (Section 9)
promptGiveawayContest claimText MEANS
  CONCAT
    "REGULATORY TEST: Giveaways/Sweepstakes/Contests (Manual Section 9)\n",
    "Context: Thai Cosmetics Manual BE 2567, Section 9\n\n",
    "Principle: Advertising with giveaways, prizes by chance, or contests must obtain\n",
    "prior authorization under gambling law and clearly state all required information.\n\n",
    "Decision Boundary:\n",
    "✅ ACCEPTABLE:\n",
    "  - Prior authorization obtained from official under gambling law\n",
    "  - Clearly states: criteria, start/end dates, gift/prize details, value, area, draw details\n\n",
    "❌ PROHIBITED:\n",
    "  - No prior authorization under gambling law\n",
    "  - Missing required information\n\n",
    "Evaluate this advertising: ", claimText, "\n\n",
    "Question: Does this giveaway/sweepstakes/contest advertising LACK prior\n",
    "authorization or FAIL to clearly state required information?\n\n",
    "Answer with:\n",
    "- YES (violates giveaway rules - prohibited) or NO (complies - acceptable)\n",
    "- Confidence: [0-100]%\n",
    "- Reasoning: [1-2 sentences explaining your judgment]"

