// CATEGORY: Whitening Products
promptWhiteningNaturalTone claimText MEANS
  CONCAT
    "REGULATORY TEST: Natural Skin Tone Alteration (Whitening Products)\n",
    "Context: Thai Cosmetics Manual BE 2567, Category 1 (Whitening Products)\n\n",
    "Principle: Whitening cosmetics can only affect APPEARANCE during use (temporary\n",
    "cosmetic effect), not ALTER natural skin color (physiological change).\n\n",
    "Decision Boundary:\n",
    "✅ ACCEPTABLE: \"appears radiant\", \"appears fair\", \"looks brighter\" (temporary appearance)\n",
    "❌ PROHIBITED: \"changes natural skin color\", \"whitens by X levels\", \"lightens skin tone\",\n",
    "    \"reduces melanin\" (physiological alteration)\n\n",
    "Key distinction: Measurable changes (\"5 levels\", \"3 shades lighter\") imply\n",
    "physiological alteration, not temporary cosmetic appearance.\n\n",
    "Evaluate this claim: ", claimText, "\n\n",
    "Question: Does this claim imply ALTERATION of natural skin tone (physiological\n",
    "change, measurable change, or permanent change) rather than temporary cosmetic\n",
    "APPEARANCE?\n\n",
    "Answer with:\n",
    "- YES (prohibited) or NO (acceptable)\n",
    "- Confidence: [0-100]%\n",
    "- Reasoning: [1-2 sentences explaining your judgment]"

