    "  - \"deep nourishment to hair roots\"\n",
    "  - \"nourish hair root / helps to strengthen hair root\"\n",
    "  - \"nourishes hair / helps hair stay strong from the root to tip\" (if\n",
    "    interpreted as structural/medical)\n",
    "  - Any claim implying effect on roots located in dermis\n\n",
    "Key distinction: Surface cosmetic nourishment ✓ vs. deep structural nourishment of roots ✗\n\n",
    "Evaluate this claim: ", claimText, "\n\n",
    "Question: Does this claim imply DEEP NOURISHMENT TO HAIR ROOTS or effects on\n",
    "hair root structures in the dermis, rather than surface cosmetic conditioning?\n\n",
    "Answer with:\n",
    "- YES (violates hair care rules - prohibited) or NO (acceptable)\n",
