// CATEGORY: Natural Products
promptNaturalFalseClaims claimText MEANS
  CONCAT
    "REGULATORY TEST: False Natural/No-Chemical Claims (Natural Category)\n",
    "Context: Thai Cosmetics Manual BE 2567, Category 19 (Natural Products), p.42\n\n",
    "Principle: Cosmetics may use \"Made from natural ingredients\" ONLY IF all\n",
    "components are from natural sources without extraction processes (except size\n",
    "reduction) and without preservatives. May use \"Contains natural ingredients or\n",
    "extracts\" if cosmetic contains SOME natural-sourced ingredients. Cannot use\n",
    "natural or no-chemical claims if product contains chemical ingredients.\n\n",
    "Decision Boundary:\n",
    "✅ ACCEPTABLE (accurate natural claims):\n",
    "  - \"Made from natural ingredients\" ONLY IF: all components from natural\n",
    "    sources, no extraction processes (except size reduction), no preservatives\n",
    "    (e.g., henna powder + green tea powder)\n",
    "  - \"Contains natural ingredients or extracts\" if contains SOME natural-sourced\n",
    "    ingredients (e.g., contains Centella asiatica extract)\n\n",
    "❌ PROHIBITED (false natural/no-chemical claims):\n",
    "  - \"Made from natural ingredients\" if product contains chemical ingredients\n",
    "  - \"No chemical additives\" if product contains chemical ingredients\n",
    "  - \"100% natural\" if not fully compliant\n",
    "  - Any false natural claim\n\n",
    "Key distinction: Accurate natural claims based on formula ✓ vs. false natural claims ✗\n\n",
    "Evaluate this claim: ", claimText, "\n\n",
    "Question: Does this claim assert \"MADE FROM NATURAL INGREDIENTS\" or \"NO\n",
    "CHEMICAL ADDITIVES\" when the product CONTAINS CHEMICAL INGREDIENTS?\n\n",
    "Answer with:\n",
    "- YES (violates natural product rules - prohibited) or NO (acceptable)\n",
    "- UNKNOWN (cannot determine formula)\n",
    "- Confidence: [0-100]%\n",
    "- Reasoning: [1-2 sentences explaining your judgment]"

